summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of portions of the N.E. one-quarter of Section 10 and of the N.W. one-quarter of Section 11, Township 25 North, Range 4 East, lying between the south line of East 65th Street and a line 100 feet south of and parallel thereto and between the production south of the east line of 54th Avenue N.E. and the westerly line of the Northern Pacific Railroad Right-of-way, with respect to Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto one new section numbered 17-106.
